@startuml
title **传感器数据采集、处理与同步流程**\n（阶段二～阶段四）

' 阶段二：模拟采集与存储（任务 T-009, T-010, T-011, T-013）
box "阶段二：传感器模拟采集与存储" #LightBlue
    actor 用户
    participant "HeartRateCollector\n(T-009)" as Collector
    participant "AccelerometerCollector\n(T-010)" as AccCollector
    participant "SensorDataRepository\n(T-011)" as Repo
    participant "Room Database\n(T-025~T-034)" as DB
end box

' 阶段三：处理流水线（任务 T-015~T-024）
box "阶段三：数据处理流水线" #LightGreen
    participant "ProcessorRegistry\n(T-020)" as Registry
    participant "ProcessorChain\n(T-019)" as Chain
    participant "DataProcessor(s)\n(T-021, T-022)" as Processor
end box

' 阶段四：同步到云端（任务 T-012, T-039, T-040）
box "阶段四：WorkManager 上传" #LightYellow
    participant "SyncWorker\n(T-040)" as Sync
    participant "Netlify Server" as Server
end box

' 时序流程
用户 -> Collector: 启动采集 (T-009)
Collector -> Collector: 每秒产生 RawHeartRate
Collector -> Repo: insertRawData(raw)
Repo -> DB: 存储 RawDataEntity

用户 -> AccCollector: 启动采集 (T-010)
AccCollector -> AccCollector: 模拟加速度数据
AccCollector -> Repo: insertRawData(raw)

Repo -> Registry: getChain(RawHeartRate::class)
Registry --> Repo: ProcessorChain
Repo -> Chain: execute(raw)
Chain -> Processor: 平滑处理 (T-021)
Processor --> Chain: SmoothedHeartRate
Chain -> Processor: 分析处理 (T-022)
Processor --> Chain: HeartRateAlert
Chain --> Repo: 最终 ConsumableData
Repo -> DB: 存储 ConsumableDataEntity

' 同步触发
Repo -> Sync: 触发同步 (T-040)
Sync -> DB: 读取未同步数据
DB --> Sync: 返回数据列表
Sync -> Server: POST /api/sync (T-035)
Server --> Sync: 200 OK
Sync -> DB: 更新 synced 标志

@enduml